description:
🎄 PyData Bristol Xmas Social (Joint with Data Bristol!)🎄

It has been a great year and we are going to wrap it up with a festive social event. Please come and join us at the The Famous Royal Navy Volunteer,
17-18 King Street, Bristol!

Our social will be held jointly with Data Bristol - See their event here: https://www.meetup.com/databristol/events/290007148/

If you're planning to come and haven't joined us previously, I'll have a 'Data Bristol' meetup sign out on a table/please message me or post in the discussion for this meetup with any questions.

We will be starting up again next year so if you would like to speak at January’s or a future event - please fill out this form: https://goo.gl/forms/8lsz1WA1986Ahbbs1

# 🕖 LOGISTICS

We will meeting at The Knights Templar, You should be able to spot the organisers there.
If you realise you can't make it, please un-RSVP in good time so we know roughly how many of us will be there.
Follow @pydatabristol (https://twitter.com/pydatabristol) for updates on this and future events, as well as news from the global PyData community.

# 📜 CODE OF CONDUCT

The PyData Code of Conduct governs this meetup (https://pydata.org/code-of-conduct/). To discuss any issues or concerns relating to the code of conduct or behavior of anyone at the PyData meetup, please contact the PyData Bristol organisers, or you can submit a report of any potential Code of Conduct violation directly to NumFOCUS (https://numfocus.typeform.com/to/ynjGdT).
title: PyData Bristol - Xmas Social 🎄 (Joint with Data Bristol!)
